                                                                                                                    <div class="card">
                                            <div class="card-header" id="card-method_1">
                                                <a href="javascript:void(0);" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#tab-method_1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                                    Method                                                </a>
                                            </div>

                                            <div id="tab-method_1" class="collapse " aria-labelledby="card-method_1" data-parent="">
                                                <div class="card-body">
                                                    <h4>Biscuits</h4>
<ol>
<li>Scale cookie mix and margarine into a mixer and beat until fat is dispersed evenly.</li>
<li>Add water and mix on slow until a dough forms. <em>(Optional: blend in pumpkin spice powder at this stage for spiced biscuits.)</em></li>
<li>Shape into 60 g pucks, place evenly spaced on trays.</li>
<li>Freeze for at least 15 minutes</li>
<li>Bake from frozen at 160°C for 12 minutes. Allow to cool on tray until set.</li>
</ol>
<h4></h4>
<h4>Assembly</h4>
<ol>
<li>Fold pumpkin spice powder into Ready-to-Use Mallow until evenly dispersed.</li>
<li>Pipe or spread a layer of spiced mallow onto the flat side of one biscuit.</li>
<li>Drizzle or spread a little melted dark chocolate over the mallow.</li>
<li>Sandwich with a second biscuit.</li>
<li>Optionally finish with an extra drizzle of dark chocolate across the top for decoration.</li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Yield: 20 cookies= 10 s’mores</p>
